  <entry>
    <title>Play with yolov8</title>
    <link href="https://heyeuu.github.io/2025/04/04/play-with-yolov8/"/>
    <id>https://heyeuu.github.io/2025/04/04/play-with-yolov8/</id>
    <published>2025-04-04T00:01:20.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-04-16T19:46:41.804Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>废话少说，先记录一下流程以便复现<br>[上网页] (<a href="https://docs.ultralytics.com/),%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BBget">https://docs.ultralytics.com/),点击get</a> start，俺是直接拉了个镜像，有了环境后，点击左侧标题栏中Task中Pose（根据需求叭）<br>对于Train,提供CLI：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>Build a new model from YAML and start training from scratch</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yolo pose train data=coco8-pose.yaml model=yolo11n-pose.yaml epochs=100 imgsz=640</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># Start training from a pretrained *.pt model</span><br><span class="line">yolo pose train data=coco8-pose.yaml model=yolo11n-pose.pt epochs=100 imgsz=640</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># Build a new model from YAML, transfer pretrained weights to it and start training</span><br><span class="line">yolo pose train data=coco8-pose.yaml model=yolo11n-pose.yaml pretrained=yolo11n-pose.pt epochs=100 imgsz=640</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>data</code>为指明数据集有关信息的配置文件，like this:</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Train/val/test sets as 1) dir: path/to/imgs, 2) file: path/to/imgs.txt, or 3) list: [path/to/imgs1, path/to/imgs2, ..]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">path:</span> <span class="string">/root/workspace/datasets</span> <span class="comment"># dataset root dir (absolute or relative; if relative, it&#x27;s relative to default datasets_dir)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">train:</span> <span class="string">images/train</span> <span class="comment"># train images (relative to &#x27;path&#x27;) 4 images</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">val:</span> <span class="string">images/val</span> <span class="comment"># val images (relative to &#x27;path&#x27;) 4 images</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">test:</span> <span class="comment"># test images (optional)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">kpt_shape:</span> [<span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">2</span>] <span class="comment"># number of keypoints, number of dims (2 for x,y or 3 for x,y,visible)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># flip_idx: [0, 2, 1, 4, 3, 6, 5, 8, 7, 10, 9, 12, 11, 14, 13, 16, 15]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">nc:</span> <span class="number">14</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">names:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">0:</span> <span class="string">B1</span> </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">1:</span> <span class="string">B2</span> </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">2:</span> <span class="string">B3</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">3:</span> <span class="string">B4</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">4:</span> <span class="string">B5</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">5:</span> <span class="string">BO</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">6:</span> <span class="string">BS</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">7:</span> <span class="string">R1</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">8:</span> <span class="string">R2</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">9:</span> <span class="string">R3</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">10:</span> <span class="string">R4</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">11:</span> <span class="string">R5</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">12:</span> <span class="string">RO</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">13:</span> <span class="string">RS</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>maybe 会使用到这个指令：</p><figure class="highlight zsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ yolo pose train data=armor_kpt.yaml model=yolo11n-pose.pt epochs=1 imgsz=640 device=0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>but 具体参数得改改<br>然后会得到一些反馈，其中有一句，类似这样子：</p><figure class="highlight zsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ Results saved to /ultralytics/runs/pose/train5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>那么在之后测试时，可能会用到类似于这样的指令：</p><figure class="highlight zsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yolo val model=/ultralytics/runs/pose/train5/weights/best.pt data=armor_kpt.yaml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里想强调的是，记得把model换成刚刚训练的模型，就在刚才那句<code>Results saved to /ultralytics/runs/pose/train5</code>里<br>剩下predict、export、track啥的还没试，晚点说，就这样<br>现在只想随心记录下来，格式下次再说<br>Hello world！</p><h6 id="特别鸣谢：lsy"><a href="#特别鸣谢：lsy" class="headerlink" title="特别鸣谢：lsy"></a>特别鸣谢：lsy</h6>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;废话少说，先记录一下流程以便复现&lt;br&gt;[上网页] (&lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.ultralytics.com/),%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BBget&quot;&gt;https://docs.ultralytics.com/),点击get&lt;/a&gt; start，</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
